tags.name: Stringfellow Court
tags.note: TIGER had the name misspelled (Strongfellow is incorrect; Stringfellow is correct).

tags.name: 600 East
tags.note: Due to traffic circulation patterns in this area necessitated by the one-way on 600 S and the median on 400 S, the northbound lane of 600 E is MUCH more important than the southbound lane to the road network. That's why the northbound lane is tertiary.

tags.name: Gallivan Avenue
tags.note: The North-South part of this road is Weechquootee Place; the East-West part is Gallivan Avenue.
